{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/PowerOfTheElegems2.png?t=1739406061\" /><br>The legendary Elegems are special gems that tap into natural energy. The gems hold the key to unlock unimaginable abilities and unravel the secrets of Morrok. With the Elegems, Aruma is able to cast magic spells and enhance her mighty fist.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/ElemdianPowerOfElegem.gif?t=1739406061\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/ElemdianUnleashTheWolf.png?t=1739406061\" /><br>Aruma possesses a unique ability bestowed upon her by her wolf heritage: the power to transform into a majestic wolf at will. This remarkable gift grants her the ability to speed through landscapes, leap across chasms, and unveil hidden secrets scattered throughout the kingdom.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/ElemdianTransformation.gif?t=1739406061\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/ElemdianExplore.png?t=1739406061\" /><br>Sprint, scale heights or harness the Power of Elegems and teleport or Soar Across Enchanted Islands. Uncover hidden wonders and unravel the mysteries of Morrok.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/ElemdianExploration.gif?t=1739406061\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553330/extras/ElemdianMasterSpellCrafting.png?t=1739406061\" /><br>Master the art of Spell Crafting by gathering materials from defeating foes, mining points or bought from shops. The art of Spell Crafting harnesses the energy of the Elegems and combines